}\n', '15 const double pi = acos(-1.0);\n', '16 double cal(double theta) {\n', '17   if (theta >= pi) theta -= 2 * pi;\n', '18   if (theta <= -pi) theta += 2 * pi;\n', '19   return theta;\n', '20 }\n', '21 int check(double r) {\n', '22   int num = 0;\n', '23   int tk = k;\n', '24   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 char s[10];\n', '3 int len, ans;\n', '4 void dfs(int pos, int cur, int x) {\n', '5   if (pos == len) {\n', '6     if (cur % 25 == 0) ++ans;\n', '7     return;\n', '8   }\n', '9   if (pos && cur == 0) return;\n', ""10   if (s[pos] == 'X') {\n"", '11     if (x != -1)\n', '12       dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + x, x);\n', '13     else {\n', '14       for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i) dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + i, i);\n', '15     }\n', ""16   } else if (s[pos] == '_') {\n"", '17     for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i) dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + i, x);\n', '18   } else\n', '19     dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + (s[pos] ^ 48), x);\n', '20 }\n', '21 int main() {\n', '22   scanf(""%s"", s);\n', '23   len = strlen(s);\n', '24   dfs(0, 0, -1);\n', '25   printf(""%d\\n"", ans);\n', '26   return 0;\n', '27 }\n']"	"['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 char s[10];\n', '3 int len, ans;\n', '4 void dfs(int pos, int cur, int x) {\n', '5   if (pos == len) {\n', '6     if (cur % 25 == 0) ++ans;\n', '7     return;\n', '8   }\n', '9   if (pos && cur == 0) return;\n', ""10   if (s[pos] == 'X') {\n"", '11     if (x != -1)\n', '12       dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + x, x);\n', '13     else {\n', '14       for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i) dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + i, i);\n', '15     }\n', ""16   } else if (s[pos] == '_') {\n"", '17     for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i) dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + i, i);\n', '18   } else\n', '19     dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + (s[pos] ^ 48), x);\n', '20 }\n', '21 int main() {\n', '22   scanf(""%s"", s);\n', '23   len = strlen(s);\n', '24   dfs(0, 0, -1);\n', '25   printf(""%d\\n"", ans);\n', '26   return 0;\n', '27 }\n']"	"17     for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i) dfs(pos + 1, cur * 10 + i, x);

['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int M = 1000000007;\n', '4 const int maxn = 1e5 + 10;\n', '5 map<int, int> A, B;\n', '6 long long k, f[maxn], p[maxn], jc[maxn], s[maxn];\n', '7 int n, m;\n', '8 long long pow_(long long x, long long y) {\n', '9   long long ret = 1;\n', '10   while (y) {\n', '11     if (y & 1) ret = ret * x % M;\n', '12     x = x * x % M;\n', '13     y >>= 1;\n', '14   }\n', '15   return ret;\n', '16 }\n', '17 long long inv(long long x) { return pow_(x, M - 2); }\n', '18 long long C(int x, int y) { return jc[x] * inv(jc[y] * jc[x - y] % M) % M; }\n', '19 long long solve(int x) {\n', '20   if (B.find(x) != B.end()) return B[x];\n', '21   long long ret = 0;\n', '22   for (int i = 0; i <= m; i++) ret = (ret + p[i] * s[x + i]) % M;\n', '23   return B[x] = ret;\n', '24 }\n', '25 int main() {\n', '26   cin >> n >> k;\n', '27   jc[0] = 1;\n', '28   for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) jc[i] = jc[i - 1] * i % M;\n', '29   for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {\n', '30     int x;\n', '31     cin >> x;\n', '32     A[x]++;\n', '33   }\n', '34   f[0] = k - 1;\n', '35   for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) {\n', '36     long long p = inv(n) * i % M;\n', '37     long long q = inv(n) * (n - i) % M * inv(k - 1) % M;\n', '38     f[i] = (p * f[i - 1] + 1) % M * inv(q) % M;\n', '39   }\n', '40   s[n] = 0;\n', '41   for (int i = n; i; i--) s[i - 1] = (s[i] + f[i - 1]) % M;\n', '42   m = A[-1];\n', '43   for (int i = 0; i <= m; i++)\n', '44     p[i] = C(m, i) * pow_(k - 1, m - i) % M * inv(pow_(k, m)) % M;\n', '45   long long tot = k;\n', '46   long long ans = 0;\n', '47   for (auto x : A) {\n', '48     if (x.first == -1) continue;\n', '49     ans = (ans + solve(x.second)) % M;\n', '50     tot--;\n', '51   }\n', '52   ans = (ans + tot * solve(0)) % M;\n', '53   ans = (ans - (k - 1) * s[0]) % M;\n', '54   ans = ans * inv(k - 1) % M;\n', '55   cout << (ans + M) % M << endl;\n', '56 }\n']	['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int M = 1000000007;\n', '4 const int maxn = 1e5 + 10;\n', '5 map<int, int> A, B;\n', '6 long long k, f[maxn], p[maxn], jc[maxn], s[maxn];\n', '7 int n, m;\n', '8 long long pow_(long long x, long long y) {\n', '9   long long ret = 1;\n', '10   while (y) {\n', '11     if (y & 1) ret = ret * x % M;\n', '12     x = x * x % M;\n', '13     y >>= 1;\n', '14   }\n', '15   return ret;\n', '16 }\n', '17 long long inv(long long x) { return pow_(x, M - 2); "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 1e5 + 50;\n', '4 int n, q, dfn[N], rr[N], cnt, f[N][20], d[N], a[N];\n', '5 long long bit[N];\n', '6 vector<int> v[N];\n', '7 void dfs(int x, int ff) {\n', '8   dfn[x] = ++cnt;\n', '9   f[x][0] = ff;\n', '10   d[x] = d[ff] + 1;\n', '11   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int NMAX = 1000;\n', '4 int N, M, K;\n', '5 int a[NMAX + 2][NMAX + 2];\n', '6 struct state {\n', '7   int dad, sz;\n', '8   int down;\n', '9 };\n', '10 state ds[NMAX + 2][NMAX + 2];\n', '11 bool active[NMAX + 2][NMAX + 2];\n', '12 int root(int col, int p) {\n', '13   if (ds[p][col].dad != p) {\n', '14     return ds[p][col].dad = root(col, ds[p][col].dad);\n', '15   }\n', '16   return p;\n', '17 }\n', '18 void join(int col, int p, int q) {\n', '19   p = root(col, p);\n', '20   q = root(col, q);\n', '21   if (ds[p][col].sz > ds[q][col].sz) {\n', '22     swap(p, q);\n', '23   }\n', '24   ds[p][col].dad = q;\n', '25   ds[q][col].sz += ds[p][col].sz;\n', '26   ds[q][col].down = max(ds[q][col].down, ds[p][col].down);\n', '27 }\n', '28 int main() {\n', '29   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '30   cin.tie(nullptr);\n', '31   cin >> N >> M >> K;\n', '32   for (int i = 1; ['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 struct FenwickTree2D {\n', '4   vector<vector<int>> nodes;\n', '5   vector<vector<int>> f;\n', '6   int n;\n', '7   FenwickTree2D() {}\n', '8   FenwickTree2D(int n) : n(n) {\n', '9     nodes.resize(n + 1);\n', '10     f.resize(n + 1);\n', '11   }\n', '12   void fakeUpdate(int u, int v) {\n', '13     if (u == 0 || v == 0) {\n', '14       return;\n', '15     }\n', '16     for (int x = u; x <= n; x += x & -x) {\n', '17       nodes[x].push_back(v);\n', '18     }\n', '19   }\n', '20   void fakeGet(int u, int v) {\n', '21     if (u == 0 || v == 0) {\n', '22       return;\n', '23     }\n', '24     for (int x = u; x <= n; x += x & -x) {\n', '31       for (int y = lower_bound(nodes[x].begin(), nodes[x].end(), v) -\n', '32                    nodes[x].begin() + 1;\n', '33            y <= nodes[x].size(); y += y & -y) {\n', '34         f[x][y] = max(f[x][y], delta);\n', '35       }\n', '36     }\n', '37   }\n', '38   int get(int u, int v) {\n', '39     if (u == 0 || v == 0) {\n', '40       return 0;\n', '41     }\n', '42     int res = 0;\n', '43     for (int x = u; x > 0; x -= x & -x)\n', '44       for (int y = upper_bound(nodes[x].begin(), nodes[x].end(), v) -\n', '45                    nodes[x].begin();\n', '46            y > 0; y -= y & -y)\n', '47         res = max(res, f[x][y]);\n', '48     return res;\n', '49   }\n', '50   void build() {\n', '51     for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 long long n, m, ans;\n', '4 long long dis[2010][2010], c[2010][2010];\n', '5 char s[2010][2010];\n', '6 inline void solve(long long row, long long tl, long long tr, long long l,\n', '7                   long long r) {\n', '8   if (l > r) return;\n', '9   long long mid = (l + r) >> 1;\n', '10   dis[row][mid] = 1000000000;\n', '11   long long t = tl;\n', '12   for (long long i = tl; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int Nmax = 2e5 + 5;\n', '4 const int Mod = 666013;\n', '5 const int oo = 1e9 + 1;\n', '6 int T;\n', '7 int main() {\n', '8   cin >> T;\n', '9   while (T--) {\n', '10     int n;\n', '11     vector<pair<int, int> > v;\n', '12     cin >> n;\n', '13     int sum = 0;\n', '14     for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 namespace fast_read {\n', '4 char gc(void) {\n', '5   const int S = 1 << 17;\n', '6   static char buf[S], *s = buf, *t = buf;\n', '7   if (s == t) t = buf + fread(s = buf, 1, S, stdin);\n', '8   if (s == t) return EOF;\n', '9   return *s++;\n', '10 }\n', '11 long long RD(void) {\n', '12   long long a = 0, b = 1, c = gc();\n', ""13   for (; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long N = 5e5 + 7;\n', '4 const long long M = 1e6 + 7;\n', '5 const long long mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '6 const long long INF = 0x3f3f3f3f;\n', '7 const double eps = 1e-6;\n', '8 long long t, n, tot = 0;\n', '9 long long arr[N], lsh[N], tree[N << 1];\n', '10 inline void pushup(long long node) {\n', '11   tree[node] = tree[node << 1] + tree[node << 1 | 1];\n', '12 }\n', '13 void build(long long node, long long l, long long r) {\n', '14   if (l == r) {\n', '15     tree[node] = 0;\n', '16     return;\n', '17   }\n', '18   long long mid = l + r >> 1;\n', '19   build(node << 1, l, mid), build(node << 1 | 1, mid + 1, r);\n', '20   pushup(node);\n', '21 }\n', '22 void Updata(long long node, long long l, long long r, long long pos,\n', '23             long long val) {\n', '24   if (l == r) {\n', '25     tree[node] += val;\n', '26     return;\n', '27   }\n', '28   long long mid = l + r >> 1;\n', '29   if (pos <= mid)\n', '30     Updata(node << 1, l, mid, pos, val);\n', '31   else\n', '32     Updata(node << 1 | 1, mid + 1, r, pos, val);\n', '33   pushup(node);\n', '34 }\n', '35 long long quary(long long node, long long l, long long r, long long ql,\n', '36                 long long qr) {\n', '37   if (!ql || ql > qr) return 0;\n', '38   if (ql <= l && r <= qr) return tree[node];\n', '39   long long mid = l + r >> 1;\n', '40   long long ans = 0;\n', '41   if (ql <= mid) ans += quary(node << 1, l, mid, ql, qr);\n', '42   if (qr > mid) ans += quary(node << 1 | 1, mid + 1, r, ql, qr);\n', '43   return ans;\n', '44 }\n', '45 long long getid(long long val) {\n', '46   return lower_bound(lsh + 1, lsh + 1 + tot, val) - ['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int st_size;\n', '4 vector<int> st;\n', '5 void modi(int p, int v) {\n', '6   for (st[p += st_size / 2] += v; p > 1; p >>= 1)\n', '7     st[p >> 1] = st[p] + st[p ^ 1];\n', '8 }\n', '9 int sum(int l, int r) {\n', '10   int res = 0;\n', '11   for (l += st_size / 2, r += st_size / 2; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 using ii = pair<long long, long long>;\n', '5 long long power(long long x, long long y) {\n', '6   long long res = 1;\n', '7   while (y) {\n', '8     if (y & 1) res = (res * x) % mod;\n', '9     y = y / 2, x = (x * x) % mod;\n', '10   }\n', '11   return res % mod;\n', '12 }\n', '13 long long "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 1e6 + 10;\n', '4 const int INF = 10000000;\n', '5 void work() {\n', '6   int n, d;\n', '7   cin >> n >> d;\n', '8   vector<int> a(n, 0);\n', '9   vector<int> st(n, false);\n', '10   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 #pragma GCC optimize(""Ofast"")\n', '4 #pragma GCC target(""avx,avx2,sse,sse2,sse3,sse4,popcnt,fma"")\n', '5 #pragma GCC optimize(""unroll-loops"")\n', '6 void prepareIO() {\n', '7   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '8   cin.tie(NULL);\n', '9   cout.precision(std::numeric_limits<double>::max_digits10);\n', '10 }\n', '11 struct HASH {\n', '12   size_t operator()(const pair<long long int, long long int>& x) const {\n', '13     return hash<long long>()(x.first ^ (x.second) << 32);\n', '14   }\n', '15 };\n', '16 const long long int MOD = 1e9 + 7;\n', '17 const long long int N = 1e5 + 5;\n', '18 void dfs(long long int u, long long int st, vector<long long int>& a,\n', '19          vector<long long int>& adj, vector<bool>& vis, long long int& ans,\n', '20          bool& notPoss) {\n', '21   if (a[u] == 0) {\n', '22     vis[u] = true;\n', '23     return;\n', '24   }\n', '25   long long int v = adj[u];\n', '26   if (vis[v] && v == st) {\n', '27     notPoss = true;\n', '28     return;\n', '29   }\n', '30   vis[u] = true;\n', '31   ans++;\n', '32   dfs(v, st, a, adj, vis, ans, notPoss);\n', '33 }\n', '34 int main() {\n', '35   prepareIO();\n', '36   long long int t = 1;\n', '37   cin >> t;\n', '38   for (long long int Case = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 2e4 + 100, INF = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 int kase, n, a[N], s[2100], t[2100];\n', '5 bool check(int x) {\n', '6   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 #pragma GCC optimize(""Ofast,unroll-loops,no-stack-protector,fast-math"")\n', '3 using namespace std;\n', '4 const int INF = 1e9;\n', '5 void solve() {\n', '6   int n;\n', '7   cin >> n;\n', '8   vector<int> a(n);\n', '9   for (int& i : a) cin >> i;\n', '10   const int mx = *max_element(a.begin(), a.end()) << 1;\n', '11   vector<int> dp(mx + 1, INF);\n', '12   dp[0] = 0;\n', '13   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 103;\n', '4 int n, P;\n', '5 int f[N][N][N], fc[N], C[N][N];\n', '6 inline int add(const int &a, const int &b) {\n', '7   return a + b >= P ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 100 + 3;\n', '4 int mod;\n', '5 int bigmod(int a, int b) {\n', '6   int ans = 1;\n', '7   while (b > 0) {\n', '8     if (b & 1) {\n', '9       ans = (ans * 1ll * a) % mod;\n', '10     }\n', '11     a = (a * 1ll * a) % mod;\n', '12     b >>= 1;\n', '13   }\n', '14   return ans;\n', '15 }\n', '16 inline int add(int x, int y) { return (x + y >= mod ? x + y - mod : x + y); }\n', '17 inline int sub(int x, int y) { return (x - y < 0 ? x - y + mod : x - y); }\n', '18 inline int gun(int x, int y) { return ((x * 1ll * y) % mod); }\n', '19 inline int vag(int x, int y) { return (x * 1ll * bigmod(y, mod - 2)) % mod; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long N = 1e2 + 1e1 + 7;\n', '4 long long n, m, k, P;\n', '5 long long f[N][N][N], C[N][N];\n', '6 void inc(long long &a, long long b) {\n', '7   a += b;\n', '8   a >= P ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int SQRT = 450;\n', '4 int main() {\n', '5   ios::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '6   cin.tie(nullptr);\n', '7   int n, m;\n', '8   cin >> n >> m;\n', '9   vector<int> x(n), y(n);\n', '10   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 3e5 + 5, B = 400;\n', '4 int ans[B + 1][B + 1], pr[N], n, m, x[N], y[N], xx, yy, ty, idx, sm, add[N];\n', '5 void update(int i, int xx, int yy, int val, int idd) {\n', '6   if (xx + yy >= B) {\n', '7     for (int j = i; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 const int N = 200005, B = 505, lim = 500, blc = 500;\n', '3 int n, m, x[N], y[N], is[N], t[N];\n', '4 int sum[B][B];\n', '5 int tag[B], val[N];\n', '6 inline void add(int x, int v) {\n', '7   tag[(((x) + blc - 1) / blc)] += v, val[x] += v;\n', '8 }\n', '9 inline int ask(int x) {\n', '10   int ret = 0;\n', '11   for (int i = 1; i < (((x) + blc - 1) / blc); ++i) ret += tag[i];\n', '12   for (int i = ((((x) + blc - 1) / blc) - 1) * blc + 1; i <= x; ++i)\n', '13     ret += val[i];\n', '14   return ret;\n', '15 }\n', '16 inline void solve(int x) {\n', '17   int ans = 0;\n', '18   for (int i = 1; i <= lim; ++i) ans += sum[i][(x - 1) % i + 1];\n', '19   printf(""%d\\n"", ans + ask(x));\n', '20 }\n', '21 inline void radd(int u, int v, int t) {\n', '22   is[u] += v;\n', '23   if (x[u] + y[u] > lim) {\n', '24     int cur = t - 1;\n', '25     while (cur + x[u] < m) {\n', '26       add(cur + x[u] + 1, v);\n', '27       if (cur + x[u] + y[u] + 1 <= m) add(cur + x[u] + y[u] + 1, -v);\n', '28       cur += x[u] + y[u];\n', '29     }\n', '30   } else {\n', '31     for (int i = x[u] + 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 4010;\n', '4 int n, m, a[N], rt, tot, L[N], siz[N], R[N], ls[N], rs[N];\n', '5 long long val[N], dp[N][N];\n', '6 inline void build(int &p, int l, int r) {\n', '7   if (l > r) return;\n', '8   p = ++tot;\n', '9   int pos = l;\n', '10   for (int i = l; i <= r; ++i)\n', '11     if (a[i] < a[pos]) pos = i;\n', '12   val[p] = a[pos];\n', '13   build(ls[p], l, pos - 1);\n', '14   build(rs[p], pos + 1, r);\n', '15   dp[p][0] = 0;\n', '16   dp[p][1] = m * val[p] - val[p];\n', '17   siz[p] = 1;\n', '18   for (int i = siz[p]; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 #pragma GCC optimize(2, 3, ""Ofast"")\n', '3 using namespace std;\n', '4 template <typename T1, typename T2>\n', '5 void ckmin(T1 &a, T2 b) {\n', '6   if (a > b) a = b;\n', '7 }\n', '8 template <typename T1, typename T2>\n', '9 void ckmax(T1 &a, T2 b) {\n', '10   if (a < b) a = b;\n', '11 }\n', '12 int read() {\n', '13   int x = 0, f = 0;\n', '14   char ch = getchar();\n', ""15   while (!isdigit(ch)) f |= ch == '-', ch = getchar();\n"", ""16   while (isdigit(ch)) x = 10 * x + ch - '0', ch = getchar();\n"", '17   return f ? -x : x;\n', '18 }\n', '19 template <typename T>\n', '20 void print(T x) {\n', ""21   if (x < 0) putchar('-'), x = -x;\n"", '22   if (x >= 10) print(x / 10);\n', ""23   putchar(x % 10 + '0');\n"", '24 }\n', '25 template <typename T>\n', '26 void print(T x, char let) {\n', '27   print(x), putchar(let);\n', '28 }\n', '29 const int N = 4005;\n', '30 long long dp[N][N];\n', '31 int sz[N], a[N], n, m, tot;\n', '32 void solve(int &u, int l, int r) {\n', '33   if (l > r) {\n', '34     u = 0;\n', '35     return;\n', '36   }\n', '37   u = ++tot, sz[u] = r - l + 1;\n', '38   dp[u][0] = 0;\n', '39   dp[u][1] = 1ll * (m - 1) * a[l];\n', '40   int pos = l, ls = 0, rs = 0;\n', '41   for (int i = l; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 4005;\n', '4 int pos[N][N], ls[N], rs[N], siz[N];\n', '5 int build(int l, int r) {\n', '6   if (l == r) return l;\n', '7   int x = pos[l][r];\n', '8   if (x - 1 >= l) ls[x] = build(l, x - 1);\n', '9   if (x + 1 <= r) rs[x] = build(x + 1, r);\n', '10   return x;\n', '11 }\n', '12 int n, m;\n', '13 long long a[N], dp[N][N];\n', '14 void dfs(int x) {\n', '15   siz[x] = 1;\n', '16   if (ls[x]) dfs(ls[x]), siz[x] += siz[ls[x]];\n', '17   if (rs[x]) dfs(rs[x]), siz[x] += siz[rs[x]];\n', '18   if ((!ls[x]) && (!rs[x])) return;\n', '19   if (!ls[x]) {\n', '20     for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long N = 2e6 + 6;\n', '4 const long long P = 1e9 + 7;\n', '5 long long read() {\n', '6   long long an = 0, ff = 1;\n', '7   char c = getchar();\n', ""8   for (; c < '0' || c > '9'; c = getchar())\n"", ""9     if (c == '-') ff = -1;\n"", ""10   for (; c >= '0' && c <= '9'; c = getchar())\n"", ""11     an = (an << 3) + (an << 1) + c - '0';\n"", '12   return an * ff;\n', '13 }\n', '14 long long Add(long long a, long long b) {\n', '15   return a + b >= P ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int M = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 long long fastpower(long long x, long long n, long long M) {\n', '5   if (n == 0)\n', '6     return 1;\n', '7   else if (n % 2 == 0)\n', '8     return fastpower((x * x) % M, n / 2, M);\n', '9   else\n', '10     return (x * fastpower((x * x) % M, (n - 1) / 2, M)) % M;\n', '11 }\n', '12 long long GCD(long long A, long long B) {\n', '13   if (B == 0)\n', '14     return A;\n', '15   else\n', '16     return GCD(B, A % B);\n', '17 }\n', '18 bool vowl(char c) {\n', ""19   return c == 'a' || c == 'e' || c == 'i' || c == 'o' || c == 'u';\n"", '20 }\n', '21 long long modInverse(long long A, long long M) {\n', '22   return fastpower(A, M - 2, M);\n', '23 }\n', '24 void sieve(long long N) {\n', '25   bool isPrime[N + 1];\n', '26   for (long long i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 void solve() {\n', '4   long long n, ans = 1e9 + 7;\n', '5   string s;\n', '6   cin >> n >> s;\n', '7   bool flag = 1, f = 0;\n', '8   for (long long i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long M = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 signed long long power_binaryexp(long long a, long long b) {\n', '5   long long ans = 1;\n', '6   while (b > 0) {\n', '7     if (b & 1) {\n', '8       ans = (ans * a);\n', '9     }\n', '10     a = (a * a);\n', '11     b = b >> 1;\n', '12   }\n', '13   return ans;\n', '14 }\n', '15 signed long long binarymul(long long a, long long b) {\n', '16   long long ans = 0;\n', '17   while (b) {\n', '18     if (b & 1) {\n', '19       ans = ans + a;\n', '20     }\n', '21     a += a;\n', '22     b >>= 1;\n', '23   }\n', '24   return ans;\n', '25 }\n', '26 bool is_prime(long long n) {\n', '27   if (n <= 1) return false;\n', '28   if (n <= 3) return true;\n', '29   if (n % 2 == 0 || n % 3 == 0) return false;\n', '30   for (long long i = 5; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int n, k, tt[100005][14], i, ans, j, gg;\n', '4 void cons(int l, int r, int x, int dep) {\n', '5   if (l == r) {\n', '6     return;\n', '7   }\n', '8   int tmp = (r - l + 1) / k, cc = 0;\n', '9   for (int i = l; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 4e5 + 5, mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 int n, q, x, a[N], b[N], f[N], d[N], g[N], dp[N], t[N], ans;\n', '5 multiset<int> s;\n', '6 void M(int x, int y) {\n', '7   for (; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 const int md = 1000000007;\n', '3 inline int add(int a, int b) {\n', '4   a += b;\n', '5   if (a >= md) a -= md;\n', '6   return a;\n', '7 }\n', '8 inline int sub(int a, int b) {\n', '9   a -= b;\n', '10   if (a < 0) a += md;\n', '11   return a;\n', '12 }\n', '13 const int N = 200000;\n', '14 int t, n, s[N], ord[N << 1], suf[N], b[N << 1];\n', '15 std::pair<int, int> a[N];\n', '16 bool s_cmp(int x, int y) { return a[x].first < a[y].first; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int MAX_N = 2 * 1e5 + 7;\n', '4 const int INF = 1e10 + 7;\n', '5 const int MOD = 1e9 + 7;\n', '6 const int LOG = 22;\n', '7 long long a[MAX_N];\n', '8 int main() {\n', '9   ios::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '10   cin.tie(0);\n', '11   cout.tie(0);\n', '12   int t;\n', '13   cin >> t;\n', '14   while (t--) {\n', '15     long long n, k;\n', '16     cin >> n >> k;\n', '17     for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 8192;\n', '4 const int maxn = 1e6 + 10;\n', '5 const int mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '6 inline int read() {\n', '7   int x = 0, f = 1;\n', '8   char c = getchar();\n', ""9   while (c < '0' || c > '9') {\n"", ""10     if (c == '-') f = -1;\n"", '11     c = getchar();\n', '12   }\n', ""13   while (c >= '0' && c <= '9') {\n"", ""14     x = (x << 1) + (x << 3) + c - '0';\n"", '15     c = getchar();\n', '16   }\n', '17   return x * f;\n', '18 }\n', '19 vector<int> v[N];\n', '20 int n, m, a[maxn], b[N], st[N], rec[N], ans;\n', '21 int main() {\n', '22   n = read();\n', '23   ans = st[0] = 1;\n', '24   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int N, a[1000005], b[1000005];\n', '4 string ss;\n', '5 bool IsPrime[1000006];\n', '6 int mp[1000006], Index, Prime[1000006], L[1000006];\n', '7 vector<int> stk[1000006];\n', '8 const int mx = 1e6 + 5;\n', '9 void Pre() {\n', '10   for (int i = 2; i <= mx; i++) {\n', '11     if (!IsPrime[i]) {\n', '12       mp[i] = i;\n', '13       Prime[++Index] = i;\n', '14     }\n', '15     for (int j = 1; j <= Index && i * Prime[j] <= mx; j++) {\n', '16       IsPrime[i * Prime[j]] = true;\n', '17       mp[i * Prime[j]] = Prime[j];\n', '18       if (i % Prime[j] == 0) break;\n', '19     }\n', '20   }\n', '21 }\n', '22 void Add(int x, int pos) {\n', '23   L[pos] = pos;\n', '24   while (x > 1) {\n', '25     stk[mp[x]].push_back(pos);\n', '26     x /= mp[x];\n', '27   }\n', '28 }\n', '29 void Del(int x, int pos) {\n', '30   if (x == 1) {\n', '31     L[pos] = pos;\n', '32     return;\n', '33   }\n', '34   L[pos] = pos;\n', '35   while (x > 1) {\n', '36     if (stk[mp[x]].empty()) {\n', '37       L[pos] = 0;\n', '38       return;\n', '39     }\n', '40     L[pos] = min(L[pos], stk[mp[x]].back());\n', '41     stk[mp[x]].pop_back();\n', '42     x /= mp[x];\n', '43   }\n', '44 }\n', '45 int main() {\n', '46   Pre();\n', '47   scanf(""%d"", &N);\n', '48   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int MAXN = 205;\n', '4 const int MAXP = 20005;\n', '5 int t, n, cnt, sum;\n', '6 bool f;\n', '7 int a[MAXN];\n', '8 int prime[MAXP];\n', '9 int isPrime[MAXP];\n', '10 inline int read() {\n', '11   int x = 0;\n', '12   char c = getchar();\n', ""13   while (c > '9' || c < '0') c = getchar();\n"", ""14   while (c <= '9' && c >= '0') {\n"", ""15     x = x * 10 + c - '0';\n"", '16     c = getchar();\n', '17   }\n', '18   return x;\n', '19 }\n', '20 void doGetPrime() {\n', '21   prime[++cnt] = 2;\n', '22   isPrime[2] = 1;\n', '23   for (int i = 3; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 #pragma GCC optimize(2)\n', '4 #pragma GCC optimize(3, ""Ofast"", ""inline"")\n', '5 template <typename T>\n', '6 void inline read(T &x) {\n', '7   int f = 1;\n', '8   x = 0;\n', '9   char s = getchar();\n', ""10   while (s < '0' || s > '9') {\n"", ""11     if (s == '-') f = -1;\n"", '12     s = getchar();\n', '13   }\n', ""14   while (s <= '9' && s >= '0') x = x * 10 + (s ^ 48), s = getchar();\n"", '15   x *= f;\n', '16 }\n', '17 template <typename T>\n', '18 void inline put(T x) {\n', ""19   if (x < 0) putchar('-'), x = -x;\n"", '20   if (x > 9) put(x / 10);\n', ""21   putchar(x % 10 + '0');\n"", '22   return;\n', '23 }\n', '24 const int maxn = 1e6 + 5;\n', '25 int n, m, q;\n', '26 int vis[maxn], sum, qx[maxn], qy[maxn];\n', '27 int e[maxn], nex[maxn], h[maxn], id;\n', '28 int fa[maxn], d[maxn], st[maxn];\n', '29 void add(int x, int y) {\n', '30   e[++id] = y;\n', '31   nex[id] = h[x];\n', '32   h[x] = id;\n', '33 }\n', '34 void dfs(int x) {\n', '35   st[x] = 1;\n', '36   for (int i = h[x]; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int n, m, q;\n', '4 vector<int> graf[300005];\n', '5 int cnt[300005];\n', '6 pair<int, int> kveri[300005];\n', '7 bool vis[300005];\n', '8 int cale[300005];\n', '9 int disc[300005];\n', '10 int out[300005];\n', '11 int t;\n', '12 void dfs(int u) {\n', '13   vis[u] = true;\n', '14   disc[u] = t;\n', '15   for (int c : graf[u]) {\n', '16     if (vis[c]) continue;\n', '17     t++;\n', '18     cale[c] = u;\n', '19     dfs(c);\n', '20   }\n', '21   out[u] = t;\n', '22 }\n', '23 bool anc(int x, int y) { return disc[x] <= disc[y] && out[y] <= out[x]; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 const int md = 1000000007;\n', '3 inline int add(int a, int b) {\n', '4   a += b;\n', '5   if (a >= md) a -= md;\n', '6   return a;\n', '7 }\n', '8 inline int sub(int a, int b) {\n', '9   a -= b;\n', '10   if (a < 0) a += md;\n', '11   return a;\n', '12 }\n', '13 const int N = 200000;\n', '14 int t, n, s[N], ord[N << 1], suf[N], b[N << 1];\n', '15 std::pair<int, int> a[N];\n', '16 bool s_cmp(int x, int y) { return a[x].first < a[y].first; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int abc;\n', '4 mt19937 rnd((unsigned long long)(new char));\n', '5 int rd(int l, int r) {\n', '6   uniform_int_distribution<> ee(l, r);\n', '7   return ee(rnd);\n', '8 }\n', '9 const int mxn = 4e5 + 3, mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '10 pair<int, int> ee[mxn];\n', '11 int n, v1[mxn], v2[mxn], px[mxn], m, v0[mxn], xp[mxn];\n', '12 bool vs[mxn];\n', '13 bool cmp1(int x, int y) { return v1[x] < v1[y]; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int maxn = 500000 + 50;\n', '4 int T, n, h[maxn], f[maxn], tot, ti[maxn];\n', '5 int ans, sum;\n', '6 int main() {\n', '7   scanf(""%d"", &T);\n', '8   for (int oo = 1; oo <= T; ++oo) {\n', '9     scanf(""%d"", &n);\n', '10     tot = 0;\n', '11     vector<bool> used(n);\n', '12     vector<set<int>> gi(n), ed(n);\n', '13     vector<int> seet;\n', '14     ans = 0, sum = 0;\n', '15     for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) f[i] = 0;\n', '16     for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n', '17       scanf(""%d"", &h[i]);\n', '18       tot = max(tot, ++f[--h[i]]);\n', '19     }\n', '20     for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) ti[i] = h[i];\n', '21     sort(h, h + n);\n', '22     for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 clock_t time_p = clock();\n', '4 void time_taken() {\n', '5   time_p = clock() - time_p;\n', '6   cerr << ""Time Taken : "" << (float)(time_p) / CLOCKS_PER_SEC << ""\\n"";\n', '7 }\n', '8 const long long mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '9 const long long INF = 1e18;\n', '10 const int N = 1004;\n', '11 int dp[N][N][2];\n', '12 int main() {\n', '13   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false), cin.tie(nullptr);\n', '14   int n, m, q;\n', '15   cin >> n >> m >> q;\n', '16   vector<vector<int> > a(n, vector<int>(m));\n', '17   memset(dp, 0, sizeof(dp));\n', '18   dp[n - "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int n, m, a[1005][1005], f[1005][1005], ans;\n', '4 inline bool in(int x, int l, int r) { return l <= x && x <= r; }\n', '5 int calc(int x, int y, int dx, int dy, int t) {\n', '6   if (t == 0) dx = -dx, dy = -dy;\n', '7   int cnt = 0;\n', '8   while (in(x + dx, 1, n) && in(y + dy, 1, m)) {\n', '9     x += dx, y += dy;\n', '10     if (!a[x][y]) break;\n', '11     ++cnt;\n', '12     if (dx != 0)\n', '13       dy = dx, dx = 0;\n', '14     else\n', '15       dx = dy, dy = 0;\n', '16   }\n', '17   return cnt;\n', '18 }\n', '19 signed main() {\n', '20   int q;\n', '21   cin >> n >> m >> q;\n', '22   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int maxn = 1000005;\n', '4 int a[maxn], p[maxn], ans[maxn];\n', '5 int dfs[2 * maxn][2], freq[maxn], psum[maxn];\n', '6 int main() {\n', '7   ios::sync_with_stdio(0);\n', '8   cin.tie(0);\n', '9   int t;\n', '10   cin >> t;\n', '11   while (t--) {\n', '12     int n, q;\n', '13     cin >> n >> q;\n', '14     for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 void _io() {\n', '4   std::ios::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '5   cin.tie(0);\n', '6   cout.tie(0);\n', '7 }\n', '8 void _init();\n', '9 const int MAXN = 1000005;\n', '10 const long long mod = 998244353;\n', '11 int n, q, a[MAXN], p[MAXN], ans[MAXN];\n', '12 int occur[MAXN];\n', '13 vector<int> num[MAXN];\n', '14 vector<int> g[MAXN];\n', '15 struct NODE {\n', '16   int l, k, id;\n', '17   NODE(int a, int b, int c) : l(a), k(b), id(c) {}\n', '18 };\n', '19 vector<NODE> Q[MAXN];\n', '20 int ta[MAXN];\n', '21 void add(int k, int p) {\n', '22   if (k <= 0) return;\n', '23   for (int i = k; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 template <typename T>\n', '4 struct binary_indexed_tree {\n', '5   int N;\n', '6   vector<T> BIT;\n', '7   binary_indexed_tree(int N) : N(N), BIT(N + 1, 0) {}\n', '8   void add(int i, T x) {\n', '9     i++;\n', '10     while (i <= N) {\n', '11       BIT[i] += x;\n', '12       i += i & -i;\n', '13     }\n', '14   }\n', '15   T sum(int i) {\n', '16     T ans = 0;\n', '17     while (i > 0) {\n', '18       ans += BIT[i];\n', '19       i -= i & -i;\n', '20     }\n', '21     return ans;\n', '22   }\n', '23   T sum(int L, int R) { return sum(R) - sum(L); ['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 long long gcd(long long a, long long b) {\n', '4   if (b == 0) return a;\n', '5   return gcd(b, a % b);\n', '6 }\n', '7 long long extgcd(long long a, long long b, long long& x, long long& y) {\n', '8   if (b == 0) {\n', '9     x = 1;\n', '10     y = 0;\n', '11     return a;\n', '12   }\n', '13   long long x1, y1;\n', '14   long long d = extgcd(b, a % b, x1, y1);\n', '15   x = y1;\n', '16   y = x1 - y1 * (a / b);\n', '17   return d;\n', '18 }\n', '19 long long revrsno(long long n) {\n', '20   long long k = 0;\n', '21   vector<long long> z;\n', '22   while (n > 0) {\n', '23     z.push_back(n % 10);\n', '24     n /= 10;\n', '25   }\n', '26   for (long long i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long M = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 long long power(long long a, long long b) {\n', '5   if (b == 0) return 1;\n', '6   if (b % 2 == 0) {\n', '7     long long x = power(a, b / 2);\n', '8     return (x * x) % M;\n', '9   } else\n', '10     return (a * power(a, b - 1)) % M;\n', '11 }\n', '12 void fun() {\n', '13   long long k;\n', '14   cin >> k;\n', '15   long long n;\n', '16   cin >> n;\n', '17   map<string, int> m;\n', '18   m[""white""] = 0;\n', '19   m[""yellow""] = 1;\n', '20   m[""green""] = 2;\n', '21   m[""blue""] = 3;\n', '22   m[""red""] = 4;\n', '23   m[""orange""] = 5;\n', '24   map<long long, int> vis;\n', '25   map<long long, vector<long long>> v;\n', '26   set<long long> des;\n', '27   map<long long, int> f;\n', '28   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 int k, n;\n', '5 int qpow(int a, long long b) {\n', '6   int ans = 1;\n', '7   while (b) {\n', '8     if (b & 1) ans = 1LL * ans * a % mod;\n', '9     a = 1LL * a * a % mod;\n', '10     b >>= 1;\n', '11   }\n', '12   return ans;\n', '13 }\n', '14 map<long long, int> mp;\n', '15 map<string, int> qwq;\n', '16 map<long long, int> dp[3];\n', '17 map<long long, set<long long> > G;\n', '18 void dfs(long long u) {\n', '19   for (auto v : G[u]) dfs(v);\n', '20   for (int c = 0; c < 3; ++c) {\n', '21     if (~mp[u] && c ^ mp[u]) continue;\n', '22     dp[c][u] = ~mp[u] ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int MOD = (int)1e9 + 7;\n', '4 int trans(string s) {\n', '5   if (s == ""white"") return 0;\n', '6   if (s == ""yellow"") return 1;\n', '7   if (s == ""green"") return 2;\n', '8   if (s == ""blue"") return 3;\n', '9   if (s == ""red"") return 4;\n', '10   if (s == ""orange"") return 5;\n', '11 }\n', '12 int K, N;\n', '13 set<long long> marked;\n', '14 map<long long, int> color;\n', '15 map<long long, vector<long long> > dp;\n', '16 long long pw(long long x, long long y) {\n', '17   long long ret = 1;\n', '18   for (; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int M = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 long long k, q;\n', '5 set<long long> marked;\n', '6 map<pair<long long, int>, int> dp;\n', '7 map<long long, int> color;\n', '8 set<pair<int, int> > bad_edge = {{1, 1}, {2, 2}, {3, 3}, {4, 4},\n', '9                                  {5, 5}, {6, 6}, {1, 2}, {2, 1},\n', '10                                  {3, 4}, {4, 3}, {5, 6}, {6, 5}};\n', '11 int add(int a, int b) { return (a + b) % M; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 using ll = long long;\n', '4 int a[200005];\n', '5 int idx[200005];\n', '6 int main() {\n', '7   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '8   cin.tie(0);\n', '9   cout.tie(0);\n', '10   int tc;\n', '11   cin >> tc;\n', '12   while (tc--) {\n', '13     int n;\n', '14     cin >> n;\n', '15     ll s = 0;\n', '16     for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 clock_t time_p = clock();\n', '4 void time_taken() {\n', '5   time_p = clock() - time_p;\n', '6   cerr << ""Time Taken : "" << (float)(time_p) / CLOCKS_PER_SEC << ""\\n"";\n', '7 }\n', '8 const long long mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '9 const long long INF = 1e18;\n', '10 const int N = 1004;\n', '11 int dp[N][N][2];\n', '12 int main() {\n', '13   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false), cin.tie(nullptr);\n', '14   int n, m, q;\n', '15   cin >> n >> m >> q;\n', '16   vector<vector<int> > a(n, vector<int>(m));\n', '17   memset(dp, 0, sizeof(dp));\n', '18   dp[n - "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long N = 1005;\n', '4 long long n, m, q, ans;\n', '5 bool vizitat[N][N];\n', '6 long long dp[N][N][2];\n', '7 bool verifica(long long i, long long j) {\n', '8   if (i < 1 || j < 1 || i > n || j > m) return false;\n', '9   return true;\n', '10 }\n', '11 long long cnt(long long i, long long j) {\n', '12   long long answer = 0;\n', '13   for (long long it = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 double startTime;\n', '4 double gct() { return ((double)clock() - startTime) / CLOCKS_PER_SEC; }\n', '5 void suraj();\n', '6 int main() {\n', '7   startTime = (double)clock();\n', '8   { suraj(); "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 1e3 + 5;\n', '4 int n, m, q, ans, f[N][N][2], g[N][N];\n', '5 bool st[N][N];\n', '6 int main() {\n', '7   scanf(""%d %d %d"", &n, &m, &q);\n', '8   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) {\n', '9     for (int j = 1; j <= m; ++j) {\n', '10       f[i][j][0] = (j == 1) ? 0 : (f[i][j - 1][1] + 1);\n', '11       f[i][j][1] = (i == 1) ? 0 : (f[i - 1][j][0] + 1);\n', '12       g[i][j] = f[i][j][0] + f[i][j][1] + 1;\n', '13     }\n', '14   }\n', '15   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) {\n', '16     for (int j = 1; j <= m; ++j) {\n', '17       ans += g[i][j];\n', '18     }\n', '19   }\n', '20   for (int i = 0; i <= n; ++i) {\n', '21     st[i][0] = st[i][m + 1] = 1;\n', '22   }\n', '23   for (int i = 0; i <= m; ++i) {\n', '24     st[0][i] = st[n + 1][i] = 1;\n', '25   }\n', '26   while (q--) {\n', '27     int x, y, sign;\n', '28     scanf(""%d %d"", &x, &y);\n', '29     sign = st[x][y] ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int maxn = 5e5 + 5;\n', '4 vector<pair<int, int> > g[maxn << 2];\n', '5 int id[maxn << 2];\n', '6 int le[maxn << 2];\n', '7 int "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const double pi = acos(-1.0);\n', '4 const double eps = 1e-11;\n', '5 template <class T>\n', '6 inline void ckmin(T &a, T b) {\n', '7   a = min(a, b);\n', '8 }\n', '9 template <class T>\n', '10 inline void ckmax(T &a, T b) {\n', '11   a = max(a, b);\n', '12 }\n', '13 template <class T>\n', '14 inline T sqr(T x) {\n', '15   return x * x;\n', '16 }\n', '17 using uint = unsigned int;\n', '18 using int64 = long long;\n', '19 using uint64 = unsigned long long;\n', '20 using ipair = pair<int, int>;\n', '21 using VI = vector<int>;\n', '22 using VD = vector<double>;\n', '23 using VS = vector<string>;\n', '24 using VVI = vector<VI>;\n', '25 double choose[1024][1024];\n', '26 double calc(int n, int m) {\n', '27   double r = 0;\n', '28   for (int c1 = 0; c1 < (4); ++c1) {\n', '29     int c2 = 3 - c1;\n', '30     if (c1 <= m && c2 <= n - m) {\n', '31       double prob1 = choose[m][c1] * choose[n - m][c2];\n', '32       double prob2 = 0;\n', '33       if (c1 == 0)\n', '34         prob2 = 0;\n', '35       else if (c1 == 1)\n', '36         prob2 = 2.0 / 3.0 * 0.75;\n', '37       else\n', '38         prob2 = 1;\n', '39       r += prob1 * prob2;\n', '40     }\n', '41   }\n', '42   r /= choose[n][3];\n', '43   return r;\n', '44 }\n', '45 int main() {\n', '46   std::ios::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '47   memset(choose, 0, sizeof(choose));\n', '48   for (int i = 0; i < (1024); ++i)\n', '49     for (int j = 0; j < (i + 1); ++j)\n', '50       choose[i][j] = (j == 0 ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 inline int read() {\n', '4   bool ok = 0;\n', '5   int res = 0;\n', '6   char c;\n', ""7   while (((c = getchar()) < '0' || c > '9') && c != '-')\n"", '8     ;\n', ""9   if (c == '-')\n"", '10     ok = 1;\n', '11   else\n', '12     res = c - 48;\n', ""13   while ((c = getchar()) >= '0' && c <= '9')\n"", '14     res = (res << 3) + (res << 1) + (c - 48);\n', '15   return ok ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long MOD = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 long long binpow(long long a, long long b) {\n', '5   long long ans = 1;\n', '6   while (b) {\n', '7     if (b & 1) {\n', '8       ans = ans * a % MOD;\n', '9     }\n', '10     b /= 2;\n', '11     a = a * a % MOD;\n', '12   }\n', '13   return ans;\n', '14 }\n', '15 long long inv(long long a) { return binpow(a, MOD - 2); "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 200010;\n', '4 const double eps = 1e-10;\n', '5 struct Point {\n', '6   int x, y, id, rnk;\n', '7 } p1[N];\n', '8 int n, m, s, p;\n', '9 bool ok[N];\n', '10 double ans, tot;\n', '11 bool cmp(Point i, Point j) {\n', '12   if (i.x != j.x) return i.x < j.x;\n', '13   return i.y < j.y;\n', '14 }\n', '15 bool cmp1(Point i, Point j) { return i.rnk < j.rnk; }\n', '16 inline bool check(Point i, Point j, Point k) {\n', '17   return 1ll * (j.x - i.x) * (k.y - j.y) == 1ll * (k.x - j.x) * (j.y - i.y);\n', '18 }\n', '19 inline double dis(int i, int j) {\n', '20   return sqrt(1.0 * (p1[i].x - p1[j].x) * (p1[i].x - p1[j].x) +\n', '21               1.0 * (p1[i].y - p1[j].y) * (p1[i].y - p1[j].y));\n', '22 }\n', '23 int main() {\n', '24   scanf(""%d%d"", &n, &m);\n', '25   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) scanf(""%d%d"", &p1[i].x, &p1[i].y), p1[i].id = i;\n', '26   if (n == 3) {\n', '27     double tmp[3];\n', '28     ans = dis(1, 2) + dis(2, 3) + dis(3, 1);\n', '29     for (int i = 1, j = 0; i <= 3; ++i) {\n', '30       if (i != m) tmp[++j] = dis(i, m);\n', '31     }\n', '32     ans -= max(tmp[1], tmp[2]);\n', '33     printf(""%lf\\n"", ans);\n', '34     return 0;\n', '35   }\n', '36   sort(p1 + 1, p1 + n + 1, cmp);\n', '37   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) p1[i].rnk = i;\n', '38   p = 0;\n', '39   for (int i = 2; i < n; ++i) ok[i] = check(p1[i - 1], p1[i], p1[i + 1]);\n', '40   for (int i = 2; i < n; ++i)\n', '41     if (!ok[i - 1] && !ok[i] && !ok[i + 1]) p = i;\n', '42   if (!p && !ok[2])\n', '43     p = 1;\n', '44   else if (!p)\n', '45     p = n;\n', '46   p1[p].rnk = n + 1;\n', '47   sort(p1 + 1, p1 + n + 1, cmp1);\n', '48   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long mod = 1000000007;\n', '4 const unsigned gen_seed =\n', '5     std::chrono::system_clock::now().time_since_epoch().count();\n', '6 std::mt19937_64 gen(gen_seed);\n', '7 int n;\n', '8 std::vector<int> b;\n', '9 std::vector<int> a;\n', '10 void yes() {\n', '11   printf(""YES\\n"");\n', '12   for (auto x : a) printf(""%d "", x);\n', '13   exit(0);\n', '14 }\n', '15 void no() {\n', '16   printf(""NO\\n"");\n', '17   exit(0);\n', '18 }\n', '19 void fill(int f) {\n', '20   for (int i = f; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 long long M = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 long long power(long long a, long long b) {\n', '5   long long r = 1;\n', '6   long long o = a;\n', '7   if (b <= 0) return 1;\n', '8   while (b != 0) {\n', '9     if (b % 2)\n', '10       r = (r * o) % M, b--;\n', '11     else {\n', '12       b /= 2;\n', '13       o = (o * o) % M;\n', '14     }\n', '15   }\n', '16   return r;\n', '17 }\n', '18 void solve();\n', '19 int main() {\n', '20   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '21   cin.tie(NULL);\n', '22   cout.tie(NULL);\n', '23   long long t = 1;\n', '24   while (t--) {\n', '25     solve();\n', '26     cout << ""\\n"";\n', '27   }\n', '28   return 0;\n', '29 }\n', '30 void solve() {\n', '31   long long n;\n', '32   cin >> n;\n', '33   vector<long long> a(n);\n', '34   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 inline bool Read(int &a) { return scanf(""%d"", &a) != EOF; }\n', '4 inline bool Read(int &a, int &b) { return scanf(""%d%d"", &a, &b) != EOF; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 long long n, t, ans, i, j, m, k, a, b, z, voly, c, s[1000 * 1000 + 1],\n', '4     parent[1000 * 1000 + 1], used[1000 * 1000 + 1];\n', '5 vector<long long> v;\n', '6 void make_set(int v) {\n', '7   parent[v] = v;\n', '8   s[v] = 1;\n', '9 }\n', '10 int find_set(int v) {\n', '11   if (v == parent[v]) return v;\n', '12   return parent[v] = find_set(parent[v]);\n', '13 }\n', '14 void union_sets(int a, int b) {\n', '15   a = find_set(a);\n', '16   b = find_set(b);\n', '17   if (a != b) {\n', '18     if (s[a] < s[b]) swap(a, b);\n', '19     parent[b] = a;\n', '20     s[a] += s[b];\n', '21   }\n', '22 }\n', '23 signed main() {\n', '24   cin >> n >> m;\n', '25   for (j = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 1e3 + 10;\n', '4 int n, m, res[N * N], idx = -1, step;\n', '5 int dx[4] = {0, 1, 0, -1}, dy[4] = {-1, 0, 1, 0};\n', '6 bool book[N][N];\n', '7 int a[N][N];\n', '8 void dfs(int x, int y) {\n', '9   bool flag = 0;\n', '10   int xx = a[x][y];\n', '11   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int mxN = 1e3;\n', '4 int n, m, mp[mxN][mxN] = {0};\n', '5 bool vis[mxN][mxN] = {0};\n', '6 bool e(int i, int j) { return i >= 0 && i < n && j >= 0 && j < m && vis[i][j]; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 namespace std {}\n', '4 long long t, n, m;\n', '5 bitset<4> s[1005][1005];\n', '6 bool vis[1005][1005];\n', '7 queue<long long> Q;\n', '8 long long A[(long long)1e6 + 10], N;\n', '9 void bfs(long long x, long long y) {\n', '10   queue<pair<long long, long long>> q;\n', '11   long long cnt = 1;\n', '12   q.push({x, y});\n', '13   vis[x][y] = 1;\n', '14   while (q.size()) {\n', '15     long long a = q.front().first, b = q.front().second;\n', '16     q.pop();\n', '17     if (a - 1 >= 0 && !vis[a - 1][b] && !s[a - 1][b][1]) {\n', '18       cnt++;\n', '19       vis[a - 1][b] = 1;\n', '20       q.push({a - 1, b});\n', '21     }\n', '22     if (a + 1 < n && !vis[a + 1][b] && !s[a + 1][b][3]) {\n', '23       cnt++;\n', '24       vis[a + 1][b] = 1;\n', '25       q.push({a + 1, b});\n', '26     }\n', '27     if (b - 1 >= 0 && !vis[a][b - 1] && !s[a][b - 1][2]) {\n', '28       cnt++;\n', '29       vis[a][b - 1] = 1;\n', '30       q.push({a, b - 1});\n', '31     }\n', '32     if (b + 1 < m && !vis[a][b + 1] && !s[a][b + 1][0]) {\n', '33       cnt++;\n', '34       vis[a][b + 1] = 1;\n', '35       q.push({a, b + 1});\n', '36     }\n', '37   }\n', '38   A[N] = cnt;\n', '39   N++;\n', '40 }\n', '41 signed main() {\n', '42   ios::sync_with_stdio(0), cin.tie(0);\n', '43   cin >> n >> m;\n', '44   for (long long i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 const long long maxn = 1e6 + 10;\n', '5 long long lowbit(long long x) { return x & -x; }\n', '6 bool ispow(long long n) { return (n & (n - 1)) == 0; }\n', '7 long long fast(long long a, long long n) {\n', '8   long long base = a, res = 1;\n', '9   while (n) {\n', '10     if (n & 1) res = ((res % mod) * (base % mod)) % mod;\n', '11     base = ((base % mod) * (base % mod)) % mod;\n', '12     n >>= 1;\n', '13   }\n', '14   return res % mod;\n', '15 }\n', '16 long long las[maxn];\n', '17 string txt = ""wygbro"";\n', '18 long long dp[maxn];\n', '19 bool s[1030][1030][4];\n', '20 bool vis[1030][1030];\n', '21 long long ans[maxn], cnt;\n', '22 long long dx[] = {-1, 0, 1, 0};\n', '23 long long dy[] = {0, 1, 0, -1};\n', '24 long long dfs(long long x, long long y) {\n', '25   long long Size = 1;\n', '26   vis[x][y] = true;\n', '27   long long res = Size;\n', '28   for (long long i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int n, m;\n', '4 vector<vector<int>> a;\n', '5 bool vis[1001][1001];\n', '6 bool isNext(int i, int j, int u, int v, int dir) {\n', '7   int val1 = a[i][j], val2 = a[u][v];\n', '8   bitset<4> dir1(val1);\n', '9   bitset<4> dir2(val2);\n', '10   if (dir == 1) {\n', '11     return !dir1[1] && !dir2[3];\n', '12   } else if (dir == 2)\n', '13     return !dir1[2] && !dir2[0];\n', '14   else if (dir == 3)\n', '15     return !dir1[0] && !dir2[2];\n', '16   else\n', '17     return !dir1[3] && !dir2[1];\n', '18 }\n', '19 void dfs(int i, int j, int &sz) {\n', '20   if (i + 1 < n && !vis[i + 1][j] && isNext(i, j, i + 1, j, 1)) {\n', '21     vis[i + 1][j] = 1;\n', '22     sz++;\n', '23     dfs(i + 1, j, sz);\n', '24   }\n', '25   if (j + 1 < m && !vis[i][j + 1] && isNext(i, j, i, j + 1, 2)) {\n', '26     vis[i][j + 1] = 1;\n', '27     sz++;\n', '28     dfs(i, j + 1, sz);\n', '29   }\n', '30   if (i - 1 >= 0 && !vis[i - 1][j] && isNext(i, j, i - 1, j, 4)) {\n', '31     vis[i - 1][j] = 1;\n', '32     sz++;\n', '33     dfs(i - 1, j, sz);\n', '34   }\n', '35   if (j - 1 >= 0 && !vis[i][j - 1] && isNext(i, j, i, j - 1, 3)) {\n', '36     vis[i][j - 1] = 1;\n', '37     sz++;\n', '38     dfs(i, j - 1, sz);\n', '39   }\n', '40 }\n', '41 int main() {\n', '42   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(0);\n', '43   cin.tie(0);\n', '44   cin >> n >> m;\n', '45   a.resize(n);\n', '46   for (auto &i : a) i.resize(m);\n', '47   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int t, n, a[200005], bit[32], num;\n', '4 int gcd(int a, int b) { return b == 0 ? a : gcd(b, a % b); }\n', '5 int main() {\n', '6   cin >> t;\n', '7   while (t--) {\n', '8     cin >> n;\n', '9     memset(bit, 0, sizeof(bit));\n', '10     for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {\n', '11       cin >> num;\n', '12       int j = 1;\n', '13       while (num) {\n', '14         bit[j++] += num & 1;\n', '15         num >>= 1;\n', '16       }\n', '17     }\n', '18     int k = 0;\n', '19     for (int i = 1; i <= 31; i++) k = gcd(k, bit[i]);\n', '20     if (k == 0) {\n', '21       for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) cout << i << "" "";\n', '22     } else\n', '23       for (int i = 1; i <= k; i++) {\n', '24         if (k % i == 0) cout << i << "" "";\n', '25       }\n', '26     cout << endl;\n', '27   }\n', '28   return 0;\n', '29 }\n']"	"['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int t, n, a[200005], bit[32], num;\n', '4 int gcd(int a, int b) { b == 0 ? a : gcd(b, a % b); }\n', '5 int main() {\n', '6   cin >> t;\n', '7   while (t--) {\n', '8     cin >> n;\n', '9     memset(bit, 0, sizeof(bit));\n', '10     for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {\n', '11       cin >> num;\n', '12       int j = 1;\n', '13       while (num) {\n', '14         bit[j++] += num & 1;\n', '15         num >>= 1;\n', '16       }\n', '17     }\n', '18     int k = 0;\n', '19     for (int i = 1; i <= 31; i++) k = gcd(k, bit[i]);\n', '20     if (k == 0) {\n', '21       for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) cout << i << "" "";\n', '22     } else\n', '23       for (int i = 1; i <= k; i++) {\n', '24         if (k % i == 0) cout << i << "" "";\n', '25       }\n', '26     cout << endl;\n', '27   }\n', '28   return 0;\n', '29 }\n']"	"4 int gcd(int a, int b) { return b == 0 ? a : gcd(b, a % b); }

"['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int bits[31];\n', '4 const int P = 210000;\n', '5 map<int, int> pf[31];\n', '6 vector<int> primes;\n', '7 bool prime[P];\n', '8 void backdiv(map<int, int>::iterator i, map<int, int> &m, int val,\n', '9              vector<int> &v) {\n', '10   if (i == m.end()) {\n', '11     v.push_back(val);\n', '12     return;\n', '13   }\n', '14   for (int x = 0, val1 = val; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 long long int dfs(int i, int j, vector<vector<long long int>>& mt,\n', '4                   vector<vector<bool>>& vis) {\n', '5   int n = mt.size(), m = mt[0].size();\n', '6   if (i < 0 || i >= mt.size() || j < 0 || j >= mt[0].size()) return 0;\n', '7   vis[i][j] = true;\n', '8   int c = 1;\n', '9   for (int k = max(0, i - 1); "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int MOD = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 const int N = 3e5 + 5;\n', '5 int n, a[N], b[N], c[N], t[N];\n', '6 pair<int, int> par[N];\n', '7 void solve() {\n', '8   cin >> n;\n', '9   for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) cin >> a[i];\n', '10   for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) cin >> b[i];\n', '11   queue<int> Q;\n', '12   set<int> S;\n', '13   for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) S.insert(i), t[i] = 1e9;\n', '14   Q.push(n);\n', '15   t[n] = 1;\n', '16   int inx = -1;\n', '17   while (!Q.empty()) {\n', '18     int x = Q.front();\n', '19     Q.pop();\n', '20     int y = x - a[x];\n', '21     if (a[x] >= x) {\n', '22       inx = x;\n', '23       break;\n', '24     }\n', '25     while (!S.empty()) {\n', '26       auto it = S.lower_bound(y);\n', '27       if (it == S.end() || *it > x) break;\n', '28       if (t[*it + b[*it]] >= t[x] + 1) {\n', '29         t[*it + b[*it]] = min(t[*it + b[*it]], t[x] + 1);\n', '30         par[*it + b[*it]] = make_pair(*it, x);\n', '31         Q.push(*it + b[*it]);\n', '32       }\n', '33       S.erase(it);\n', '34     }\n', '35   }\n', ""36   cout << (t[inx] ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using ll = long long;\n', '3 int const nmax = 300000;\n', '4 int const inf = 1000000000;\n', '5 int const lgmax = 20;\n', '6 int v[5 + nmax], cost[5 + nmax];\n', '7 int far[1 + lgmax][5 + nmax];\n', '8 ll farcost[1 + lgmax][5 + nmax];\n', '9 int main() {\n', '10   std::ios::sync_with_stdio(0);\n', '11   std::cin.tie(0);\n', '12   int n, q, k;\n', '13   std::cin >> n >> q >> k;\n', '14   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 using lint = long long;\n', '4 using pi = pair<lint, lint>;\n', '5 const int MAXN = 300005;\n', '6 int n, q, k;\n', '7 lint a[MAXN], val[MAXN];\n', '8 lint minv[20][MAXN];\n', '9 int nxt[20][MAXN];\n', '10 lint dp[MAXN];\n', '11 int find_first_smaller(int x, int y) {\n', '12   if (x > n) return 1e9;\n', '13   if (minv[19][x] >= y) return 1e9;\n', '14   int ret = 0;\n', '15   for (int i = 18; i >= 0; i--) {\n', '16     if (minv[i][x] >= y) {\n', '17       ret += (1 << i);\n', '18       x += (1 << i) * k;\n', '19     }\n', '20   }\n', '21   return x;\n', '22 }\n', '23 lint shoot(int s, int x) {\n', '24   if (s > n) return 0;\n', '25   int ffs = find_first_smaller(s, x);\n', '26   int len = (n - s) / k + 1;\n', '27   if (ffs > n) return 1ll * len * x;\n', '28   return dp[ffs] + 1ll * ((ffs - s) / k) * x;\n', '29 }\n', '30 lint query(int s, int e, int x) {\n', '31   if (s > e) return 0;\n', '32   int len = (e - s) / k + 1;\n', '33   lint after_path = x;\n', '34   int pos = s;\n', '35   for (int i = 0; i < 20; i++) {\n', '36     if ((len >> i) & 1) {\n', '37       after_path = min(after_path, minv[i][pos]);\n', '38       pos += (k << i);\n', '39     }\n', '40   }\n', '41   return shoot(s, x) - shoot(pos, after_path);\n', '42 }\n', '43 int main() {\n', '44   priority_queue<pi, vector<pi>, greater<pi>> pq;\n', '45   scanf(""%d %d %d"", &n, &q, &k);\n', '46   for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {\n', '47     scanf(""%lld"", &a[i]);\n', '48     pq.emplace(a[i], i);\n', '49     while (((int)(pq).size()) && pq.top().second <= i - k) pq.pop();\n', '50     val[i] = pq.top().first;\n', '51     minv[0][i] = val[i];\n', '52     nxt[0][i] = min(i + k, n + 1);\n', '53   }\n', '54   nxt[0][n + 1] = n + 1;\n', '55   minv[0][n + 1] = 2e9;\n', '56   for (int i = 1; i < 20; i++) {\n', '57     for (int j = 1; j <= n + 1; j++) {\n', '58       minv[i][j] = min(minv[i - 1][j], minv[i - 1][nxt[i - 1][j]]);\n', '59       nxt[i][j] = nxt[i - 1][nxt[i - 1][j]];\n', '60     }\n', '61   }\n', '62   for (int i = n; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = (int)3e5 + 50, LOGN = 19;\n', '4 struct RMQ {\n', '5   int n;\n', '6   int mm[N], st[LOGN][N];\n', '7   void build(int *x) {\n', '8     mm[0] = -1;\n', '9     for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++)\n', '10       mm[i] = (i & (i - 1)) == 0 ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 300000;\n', '4 int n, cq, m, a[N + 9];\n', '5 struct question {\n', '6   int l, r, id;\n', '7   question(int L = 0, int R = 0, int Id = 0) : l(L), r(R), id(Id) {}\n', '8 } q[N + 9];\n', '9 void into() {\n', '10   scanf(""%d%d%d"", &n, &cq, &m);\n', '11   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) scanf(""%d"", &a[i]);\n', '12   for (int i = 1; i <= cq; ++i) {\n', '13     int l, r;\n', '14     scanf(""%d%d"", &l, &r);\n', '15     q[i] = question(l, r, i);\n', '16   }\n', '17 }\n', '18 int b[N + 9];\n', '19 void Get_b() {\n', '20   static int q[N + 9];\n', '21   int hd = 0, tl = 0;\n', '22   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) {\n', '23     for (; hd <= tl && a[i] <= a[q[tl]]; --tl)\n', '24       ;\n', '25     q[++tl] = i;\n', '26     for (; hd <= tl && q[hd] < i - m; ++hd)\n', '27       ;\n', '28     b[i] = a[q[hd]];\n', '29   }\n', '30 }\n', '31 vector<int> sta[N + 9], cnt[N + 9];\n', '32 vector<long long> suf[N + 9];\n', '33 long long sum[N + 9], ans[N + 9];\n', '34 void Get_ans() {\n', '35   sort(q + 1, q + cq + 1,\n', '36        [&](const question &a, const question &b) { return a.l > b.l; });\n', '37   for (int i = n, j = 1; i >= 1; --i) {\n', '38     int o = i % m;\n', '39     for (; j <= cq && q[j].l == i; ++j) {\n', '40       ans[q[j].id] = a[i];\n', '41       if (sta[o].empty()) continue;\n', '42       if (q[j].r < q[j].l + m) continue;\n', '43       int p =\n', '44           lower_bound(sta[o].begin(), sta[o].end(), q[j].r, greater<int>()) -\n', '45           sta[o].begin();\n', '46       ans[q[j].id] += sum[o] - suf[o][p] +\n', '47                       1LL * ((q[j].r - sta[o][p]) / m + 1) * b[sta[o][p]];\n', '48     }\n', '49     int c = 1;\n', '50     for (; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 static constexpr int64_t inf = 0x3f3f3f3f3f3f3f3f;\n', '4 static constexpr int Maxn = 3e5 + 5, LOG = 20;\n', '5 int n, q, k, N, Lg2[Maxn];\n', '6 int64_t a[Maxn], ans[Maxn], St[LOG][Maxn];\n', '7 inline int64_t ask(int l, int r) {\n', '8   int K = Lg2[r - l + 1];\n', '9   return min(St[K][l], St[K][r - (1 << K) + 1]);\n', '10 }\n', '11 struct Query {\n', '12   int l, r, id;\n', '13   Query() = default;\n', '14   Query(int l, int r, int id) : l(l), r(r), id(id) {}\n', '15   friend bool operator<(const Query &lhs, const Query &rhs) {\n', '16     return lhs.l != rhs.l ? lhs.l > rhs.l : lhs.r < rhs.r;\n', '17   }\n', '18 };\n', '19 vector<Query> Q[Maxn];\n', '20 struct node {\n', '21   int len;\n', '22   int64_t val, sum;\n', '23   node() = default;\n', '24   node(int l, int64_t v, int64_t s) : len(l), val(v), sum(s) {}\n', '25 } stk[Maxn];\n', '26 int lstk[Maxn];\n', '27 int top;\n', '28 void modify(int64_t v) {\n', '29   int len, slen;\n', '30   int64_t sum;\n', '31   for (len = 1; top && stk[top].val >= v;) len += stk[top--].len;\n', '32   sum = (top ? stk[top].sum : 0) + len * v;\n', '33   slen = (top ? lstk[top] : 0) + len;\n', '34   stk[++top] = node(len, v, sum);\n', '35   lstk[top] = slen;\n', '36 }\n', '37 int64_t query(int l) {\n', '38   int length = lstk[top];\n', '39   l = length - l;\n', '40   int p = upper_bound(lstk + 1, lstk + top + 1, l) - lstk - 1;\n', '41   int64_t ans = (p ? stk[p].sum : 0) + stk[p + 1].val * (l - lstk[p]);\n', '42   return stk[top].sum - ans;\n', '43 }\n', '44 int main(void) {\n', '45   scanf(""%d%d%d"", &n, &q, &k);\n', '46   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) scanf(""%lld"", &a[i]);\n', '47   Lg2[0] = -1;\n', '48   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) Lg2[i] = Lg2[i >> 1] + 1;\n', '49   for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) St[0][i] = a[i];\n', '50   for (int j = 1; j < LOG; ++j)\n', '51     for (int i = 1; i + (1 << j) - 1 <= n; ++i)\n', '52       St[j][i] = min(St[j - 1][i], St[j - 1][i + (1 << j - 1)]);\n', '53   for (int i = 1, l, r; i <= q; ++i) {\n', '54     scanf(""%d%d"", &l, &r);\n', '55     r = l + (r - l) / k * k;\n', '56     ans[i] += a[l], l += k;\n', '57     if (l <= r) Q[l % k].push_back(Query(l / k, r / k, i));\n', '58   }\n', '59   for (int mod = 0; mod < k; ++mod) {\n', '60     sort(Q[mod].begin(), Q[mod].end());\n', '61     for (top = N = 0; N * k + mod <= n; ++N)\n', '62       ;\n', '63     for (int j = N - 1, i = 0; j >= 0 && i < (int)Q[mod].size(); --j) {\n', '64       modify(ask(max(j * k + mod, 1), min((j + 1) * k + mod, n)));\n', '65       for (; i < (int)Q[mod].size() && Q[mod][i].l > j; ++i) {\n', '66         const auto &[l, r, id] = Q[mod][i];\n', '67         ans[id] += query(r - l + 1);\n', '68       }\n', '69     }\n', '70   }\n', '71   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 const long long INF = 1e16;\n', '3 const int M = 1e5 + 5;\n', '4 int n, k, tot;\n', '5 bool vis[M];\n', '6 int prime[M];\n', '7 long long phi[M], f[M][18];\n', '8 inline void Init() {\n', '9   phi[1] = 1;\n', '10   for (int i = 2; i < M; ++i) {\n', '11     if (!vis[i]) prime[++tot] = i, phi[i] = i - 1;\n', '12     for (int j = 1; j <= tot && prime[j] * i < M; ++j) {\n', '13       vis[prime[j] * i] = 1;\n', '14       if (i % prime[j] == 0) {\n', '15         phi[i * prime[j]] = phi[i] * prime[j];\n', '16         break;\n', '17       }\n', '18       phi[i * prime[j]] = phi[i] * (prime[j] - 1);\n', '19     }\n', '20   }\n', '21   for (int i = 2; i < M; ++i) phi[i] += phi[i - 1];\n', '22 }\n', '23 inline long long c(int L, int R) {\n', '24   if (L > R) return INF;\n', '25   long long res = 0;\n', '26   for (int l = L, r; l <= R; l = r + 1) {\n', '27     r = R / (R / l);\n', '28     res += 1ll * phi[R / l] * (r - l + 1);\n', '29   }\n', '30   return res;\n', '31 }\n', '32 inline void Solve(int t, int l, int r, int ql, int qr) {\n', '33   if (ql > qr || l > r) return;\n', '34   int mid = ql + qr >> 1, pos = l;\n', '35   long long val = c(std ::min(r, mid) + 1, mid);\n', '36   for (int i = std ::min(r, mid); i >= l; --i) {\n', '37     if (f[mid][t] > f[i][t - 1] + val) f[mid][t] = f[i][t - 1] + val, pos = i;\n', '38     if (val == INF)\n', '39       val = phi[mid / i];\n', '40     else\n', '41       val += phi[mid / i];\n', '42   }\n', '43   Solve(t, l, pos, ql, mid - 1);\n', '44   Solve(t, pos, r, mid + 1, qr);\n', '45 }\n', '46 inline int read() {\n', '47   int f = 1, s = 0;\n', '48   char ch = getchar();\n', ""49   while (!isdigit(ch)) (ch == '-') && (f = -1), ch = getchar();\n"", '50   while (isdigit(ch)) s = (s << 1) + (s << 3) + (ch ^ 48), ch = getchar();\n', '51   return f * s;\n', '52 }\n', '53 int main() {\n', '54   Init();\n', '55   for (int i = 0; i < 18; ++i)\n', '56     for (int j = 0; j < M; ++j) f[j][i] = INF;\n', '57   f[0][0] = 0;\n', '58   for (int i = 1; i < M; ++i) f[i][1] = 1ll * i * (i + 1) / 2;\n', '59   for (int i = 2; i < 18; ++i) Solve(i, 1, M - 5, 1, M - 5);\n', '60   int t = read();\n', '61   while (t--) {\n', '62     int n = read(), k = read();\n', '63     if (k >= 18 || (1 << k) > n) {\n', ""64       std ::cout << n << '\\n';\n"", '65       continue;\n', '66     }\n', ""67     std ::cout << f[n][k] << '\\n';\n"", '68   }\n', '69   return 0;\n', '70 }\n']"	"['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 const long long INF = 1e16;\n', '3 const int M = 1e5 + 5;\n', '4 int n, k, tot;\n', '5 bool vis[M];\n', '6 int prime[M];\n', '7 long long phi[M], f[M][18];\n', '8 inline void Init() {\n', '9   phi[1] = 1;\n', '10   for (int i = 2; i < M; ++i) {\n', '11     if (!vis[i]) prime[++tot] = i, phi[i] = i - 1;\n', '12     for (int j = 1; j <= tot && prime[j] * i < M; ++j) {\n', '13       vis[prime[j] * i] = 1;\n', '14       if (i % prime[j] == 0) {\n', '15         phi[i * prime[j]] = phi[i] * prime[j];\n', '16         break;\n', '17       }\n', '18       phi[i * prime[j]] = phi[i] * (prime[j] - 1);\n', '19     }\n', '20   }\n', '21   for (int i = 2; "
"['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int MAXN = 100010, MAXM = 1000010;\n', '4 int t, n, k, mu[MAXM], phi[MAXM];\n', '5 long long sumphi[MAXM], dp[MAXM][30];\n', '6 void solve(int l, int r, int xl, int xr, int k) {\n', '7   if (l > r) {\n', '8     return;\n', '9   }\n', '10   int mid = (l + r) >> 1, np = 0;\n', '11   long long nw = 0, nv = 1e18;\n', '12   for (int l = min(xr, mid - 1) + 2, r; l <= mid; l = r + 1) {\n', '13     r = mid / (mid / l);\n', '14     nw += sumphi[mid / l] * (r - l + 1);\n', '15   }\n', '16   for (int i = min(xr, mid - 1); i >= xl; i--) {\n', '17     nw += sumphi[mid / (i + 1)];\n', '18     if (dp[i][k - 1] + nw < nv) {\n', '19       nv = dp[i][k - 1] + nw;\n', '20       np = i;\n', '21     }\n', '22   }\n', '23   assert(xl <= np && np <= xr);\n', '24   dp[mid][k] = nv;\n', '25   solve(l, mid - 1, xl, np, k);\n', '26   solve(mid + 1, r, np, xr, k);\n', '27   return;\n', '28 }\n', '29 int main() {\n', '30   for (int i = 1; i <= MAXN - 10; i++) {\n', '31     mu[i] = 1, phi[i] = i;\n', '32     int cpi = i;\n', '33     for (int j = 2; j * j <= cpi; j++) {\n', '34       if (cpi % j == 0) {\n', '35         int cnt = 0;\n', '36         while (cpi % j == 0) {\n', '37           cpi /= j, cnt++;\n', '38         }\n', '39         if (cnt > 1) {\n', '40           mu[i] = 0;\n', '41         } else {\n', '42           mu[i] = -mu[i];\n', '43         }\n', '44         phi[i] = phi[i] / j * (j - 1);\n', '45       }\n', '46     }\n', '47     if (cpi > 1) {\n', '48       mu[i] = -mu[i], phi[i] = phi[i] / cpi * (cpi - 1);\n', '49     }\n', '50     sumphi[i] = sumphi[i - 1] + phi[i];\n', '51     dp[i][1] = 1ll * i * (i + 1) / 2;\n', '52   }\n', '53   for (int i = 2; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 15;\n', '4 int a[N];\n', '5 long long ksm(long long a, long long b, long long c) {\n', '6   int res = 1;\n', '7   while (b) {\n', '8     if (b & 1) res = (res * a) % c;\n', '9     a = (a * a) % c;\n', '10     b >>= 1;\n', '11   }\n', '12   return res % c;\n', '13 }\n', '14 int read() {\n', '15   int n;\n', '16   cin >> n;\n', '17   return n;\n', '18 }\n', '19 void solve() {\n', '20   int n;\n', '21   long long k;\n', '22   cin >> n >> k;\n', '23   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int INF = 0x3f3f3f3f;\n', '4 int main() {\n', '5   int T;\n', '6   cin >> T;\n', '7   while (T--) {\n', '8     int n, m;\n', '9     cin >> n >> m;\n', '10     vector<vector<int>> a(n, vector<int>(m));\n', '11     for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int maxn = 1e6 + 9;\n', '4 const long long MOD = 1e9 + 7;\n', '5 const int mod = 998244353;\n', '6 inline long long qpow(long long b, long long e, long long m) {\n', '7   long long a = 1;\n', '8   for (; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int maxn = 1e6 + 9;\n', '4 const long long MOD = 1e9 + 7;\n', '5 const int mod = 998244353;\n', '6 inline long long qpow(long long b, long long e, long long m) {\n', '7   long long a = 1;\n', '8   for (; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 2e5 + 10;\n', '4 const int M = 1000010;\n', '5 const int INF = 0x3f3f3f3f;\n', '6 const int mod = 998244353;\n', '7 pair<int, int> a[N], c[N];\n', '8 void solve() {\n', '9   int n, m;\n', '10   cin >> n >> m;\n', '11   long long suma = 0, sumb = 0;\n', '12   long long l = 0, r = 0;\n', '13   for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {\n', '14     cin >> a[i].first >> a[i].second;\n', '15     int first = min(m, a[i].first), second = min(m, a[i].second);\n', '16     suma += a[i].first, sumb += a[i].second;\n', '17     l += -2 * first + m, r += 2 * second - m;\n', '18   }\n', '19   if (suma + l <= sumb && suma + r >= sumb) {\n', '20     long long cx = sumb - suma - l;\n', '21     vector<pair<int, int> > res;\n', '22     for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int T, a[200010], b[200010], l[200010], r[200010];\n', '4 int main() {\n', '5   cin >> T;\n', '6   while (T--) {\n', '7     int n, m;\n', '8     cin >> n >> m;\n', '9     long long suma = 0, sumb = 0;\n', '10     for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long N = 200100;\n', '4 long long ans;\n', '5 vector<long long> a(N), b(N), m(N), ans1(N), ans2(N);\n', '6 void cal(vector<long long>& ind) {\n', '7   long long n = (long long)ind.size();\n', '8   long long l = -1, r = -1, prev = 0;\n', '9   for (long long j = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 2e5 + 5;\n', '4 long long n, a[N], b[N], m[N], cur_a[N], cur_b[N], mn[N], mx[N];\n', '5 int solve(vector<int> &v) {\n', '6   int res = 0;\n', '7   vector<pair<pair<int, int>, int> > seg;\n', '8   for (auto idx : v) {\n', '9     seg.push_back({{mx[idx], mn[idx]}, idx});\n', '10   }\n', '11   sort(seg.begin(), seg.end());\n', '12   int mxx = -1;\n', '13   for (auto it : seg) {\n', '14     int l = it.first.second, r = it.first.first, idx = it.second;\n', '15     if (l > mxx) mxx = r, res++;\n', '16     mn[idx] = mxx;\n', '17   }\n', '18   return res;\n', '19 }\n', '20 int main() {\n', '21   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(0);\n', '22   cin.tie(0);\n', '23   cout.tie(0);\n', '24   int t;\n', '25   cin >> t;\n', '26   while (t--) {\n', '27     cin >> n;\n', '28     long long sum = 0;\n', '29     map<long long, vector<int> > mp;\n', '30     for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 vector<pair<long long, long long>> vals[2000005];\n', '4 int32_t main() {\n', '5   ios::sync_with_stdio(0);\n', '6   cin.tie(0);\n', '7   long long t;\n', '8   cin >> t;\n', '9   while (t--) {\n', '10     long long n;\n', '11     cin >> n;\n', '12     pair<long long, long long> a[n];\n', '13     pair<long long, long long> op[n];\n', '14     long long mi[n];\n', '15     for (long long i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 struct Yo {\n', '4   int a, b, m, idx;\n', '5   bool operator<(const Yo &other) const {\n', '6     return (a + b - m < other.a + other.b - other.m) ||\n', '7            (a + b - m == other.a + other.b - other.m && a < other.a);\n', '8   }\n', '9 };\n', '10 int n;\n', '11 vector<pair<int, int> > ans;\n', '12 vector<Yo> v;\n', '13 void solve() {\n', '14   cin >> n;\n', '15   ans.clear();\n', '16   ans.resize(n + 1);\n', '17   v.clear();\n', '18   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int inf = 1000000000;\n', '4 long long mod = 1000000007LL;\n', '5 long long mod2 = 998244353LL;\n', '6 int t, n, h;\n', '7 int k;\n', '8 int q;\n', '9 int a[200005], b[200005];\n', '10 int m[200005];\n', '11 map<int, vector<pair<int, int>>> gp;\n', '12 vector<int> ans;\n', '13 int main() {\n', '14   cin >> t;\n', '15   for (int cas = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int max_n = 200111, inf = 1000111222, mod = 998244353;\n', '4 int f[max_n];\n', '5 int rf[max_n];\n', '6 int powm(int a, int b) {\n', '7   if (b == 0) {\n', '8     return 1;\n', '9   }\n', '10   if (b % 2 == 0) {\n', '11     return powm((1LL * a * a) % mod, b / 2);\n', '12   } else {\n', '13     return (1LL * a * powm(a, b - 1)) % mod;\n', '14   }\n', '15 }\n', '16 void precalc() {\n', '17   f[0] = 1;\n', '18   for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 #pragma GCC optimize(""O3,unroll-loops"")\n', '3 #pragma GCC target(""avx2,bmi,bmi2,lzcnt,popcnt"")\n', '4 using namespace std;\n', '5 const long long infll = (long long)1e18 + 228;\n', '6 const int inf = 1e9 + 228;\n', '7 const int mod = 998244353;\n', '8 const int MOD = 1e9 + 7;\n', '9 using mem = vector<pair<int, int>>;\n', '10 int solve(mem a, mem b, mem c) {\n', '11   sort((a).begin(), (a).end());\n', '12   sort((b).begin(), (b).end());\n', '13   sort((c).begin(), (c).end());\n', '14   int n = a.size();\n', '15   int L = 0, R = a.size() + 1;\n', '16   while (R - L > 1) {\n', '17     bool ok = 0;\n', '18     int M = (L + R) / 2;\n', '19     int p1 = M - 1;\n', '20     int p2 = inf;\n', '21     for (int i = 0; ['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int max_n = 100000;\n', '4 struct nd {\n', '5   int x, y, c;\n', '6 } a[max_n];\n', '7 int x[max_n], y[max_n], c[max_n], tmp[max_n], n, ans = 0;\n', '8 priority_queue<int> q1;\n', '9 priority_queue<int, vector<int>, greater<int> > q2;\n', '10 void lsh(int *x) {\n', '11   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = 10;\n', '4 int main() {\n', '5   int T;\n', '6   int x1, p1, x2, p2;\n', '7   cin >> T;\n', '8   string res;\n', '9   while (T--) {\n', '10     cin >> x1 >> p1 >> x2 >> p2;\n', '11     if (p2 - p1 > 6) {\n', ""12       res += '<';\n"", '13       continue;\n', '14     }\n', '15     if (p1 - p2 > 6) {\n', ""16       res += '>';\n"", '17       continue;\n', '18     }\n', '19     char s1[N] = ""\\0"", s2[N] = ""\\0"";\n', '20     int t1 = x1, t2 = x2;\n', '21     int cnt1 = 0, cnt2 = 0;\n', '22     while (t1) {\n', '23       cnt1++;\n', '24       t1 /= 10;\n', '25     }\n', '26     while (t2) {\n', '27       cnt2++;\n', '28       t2 /= 10;\n', '29     }\n', '30     int idx1 = 0, idx2 = 0;\n', '31     for (int i = cnt1 - 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 long long MAX = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 void fast() {\n', '5   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);\n', '6   cin.tie(NULL);\n', '7   cout.tie(NULL);\n', '8 }\n', '9 int gcd(int a, int b) {\n', '10   if (a == 0) return b;\n', '11   if (b == 0) return a;\n', '12   if (a == b) return a;\n', '13   if (a > b) return gcd(a - b, b);\n', '14   return gcd(a, b - a);\n', '15 }\n', '16 long long powM(long long x, long long y, long long m) {\n', '17   long long ans = 1, r = 1;\n', '18   x = x % m;\n', '19   while (r > 0 && r <= y) {\n', '20     if (r & y) {\n', '21       ans = ans * x;\n', '22       ans = ans % m;\n', '23     }\n', '24     r = r << 1;\n', '25     x = x * x;\n', '26     x = x % m;\n', '27   }\n', '28   ans = ans % m;\n', '29   return ans;\n', '30 }\n', '31 int main() {\n', '32   ios_base::sync_with_stdio(0);\n', '33   cin.tie(0);\n', '34   cout.tie(0);\n', '35   long long t;\n', '36   cin >> t;\n', '37   for (long long T = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 using ll = long long;\n', '4 const int maxn = 2e5 + 5;\n', '5 int n, m, q;\n', '6 int a[maxn], b[maxn];\n', '7 int val[2 * maxn], p[2 * ['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 long long int i, j, mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 long long int power(long long int x, long long int y, long long int mod) {\n', '5   x = x % mod;\n', '6   long long int res = 1;\n', '7   while (y) {\n', '8     if (y & 1) res = (res * x) % mod;\n', '9     y = y >> 1;\n', '10     x = (x * x) % mod;\n', '11   }\n', '12   return res % mod;\n', '13 }\n', '14 long long int modInverse(long long int n, long long int p) {\n', '15   return power(n, p - 2, p);\n', '16 }\n', '17 long long int ncr(long long int n, long long int r, long long int p) {\n', '18   if (n < r) return 0;\n', '19   if (r == 0) return 1;\n', '20   unsigned long long fac[n + 1];\n', '21   fac[0] = 1;\n', '22   for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) fac[i] = (fac[i - 1] * i) % p;\n', '23   return (fac[n] * modInverse(fac[r], p) % p * modInverse(fac[n - r], p) % p) %\n', '24          p;\n', '25 }\n', '26 long long int fact(long long int n) {\n', '27   if (n == 0) return 1;\n', '28   return n * fact(n - 1);\n', '29 }\n', '30 long long int nCr(long long int n, long long int r) {\n', '31   if (r == 2)\n', '32     return (n * (n - 1)) / 2;\n', '33   else\n', '34     return (n * (n - 1) * (n - 2)) / 6;\n', '35 }\n', '36 bool isPos(vector<vector<long long int>> &arr1, long long int mid) {\n', '37   long long int m = arr1.size(), n = arr1[0].size();\n', '38   long long int total = 0, extra = 0;\n', '39   set<long long int> sel;\n', '40   for (i = 0; ['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 uint32_t solve(size_t m, size_t n, vector<uint32_t>& data) {\n', '4   vector<bool> used;\n', '5   used.resize(m);\n', '6   bool simple = false;\n', '7   uint32_t simple_score = ~0u;\n', '8   for (size_t i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 long long ne[1000005], pre[1000005], ne300[1000005], pre300[1000005];\n', '4 void change(long long x) {\n', '5   long long k = x;\n', '6   for (long long i = 1; ['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int jump = 300;\n', '4 const int MX = 1e5 + 5;\n', '5 int p[MX], ip[MX], nxt[MX];\n', '6 void overwrite(int pos, int finish, int turns) {\n', '7   if (turns == 0) {\n', '8     return;\n', '9   }\n', '10   nxt[pos] = finish;\n', '11   overwrite(ip[pos], ip[finish], turns - 1);\n', '12 }\n', '13 void update(int pos) {\n', '14   int finish = pos;\n', '15   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 using ull = unsigned long long;\n', '4 const int N = 1e6 + 5;\n', '5 mt19937_64 rnd(time(0));\n', '6 int n, K, flag[N], pr[N], cnt;\n', '7 ull H[N], sum;\n', '8 unordered_map<ull, int> pos;\n', '9 int main() {\n', '10   scanf(""%d"", &n);\n', '11   K = n >> 1;\n', '12   flag[0] = flag[1] = 1, H[1] = 0;\n', '13   for (int i = 2; i <= n; i++) {\n', '14     if (!flag[i]) pr[++cnt] = i, H[i] = rnd();\n', '15     for (int j = 1; j <= cnt && i * pr[j] <= n; j++) {\n', '16       flag[i * pr[j]] = 1, H[i * pr[j]] = H[i] ^ H[pr[j]];\n', '17       if (i % pr[j] == 0) break;\n', '18     }\n', '19   }\n', '20   for (int i = 2; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long MOD = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 long long n, m, a, b, c, d, p;\n', '5 long long add(long long first, long long second) {\n', '6   return (first + second) % MOD;\n', '7 }\n', '8 long long sub(long long first, long long second) {\n', '9   return add(first, MOD - second);\n', '10 }\n', '11 long long mul(long long first, long long second) {\n', '12   return first * second % MOD;\n', '13 }\n', '14 long long binpow(long long first, long long second) {\n', '15   if (second == 0) return 1;\n', '16   if (second % 2) return mul(first, binpow(first, second - 1));\n', '17   long long z = binpow(first, second / 2);\n', '18   return mul(z, z);\n', '19 }\n', '20 long long inv(long long first) { return binpow(first, MOD - 2); ['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const long long mod = 1e9 + 7;\n', '4 long long ksm(long long a, long long b, long long mod) {\n', '5   long long c = 1;\n', '6   while (b) {\n', '7     if (b & 1) c = c * a % mod;\n', '8     b >>= 1;\n', '9     a = a * a % mod;\n', '10   }\n', '11   return c;\n', '12 }\n', '13 long long inv(int x) { return ksm(x, mod - 2, mod); "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = (int)2e5 + 50, LOGN = 17;\n', '4 const int INF = (int)1e9;\n', '5 int n, k;\n', '6 int ord[N], in[N], tim = 0;\n', '7 char las[N];\n', '8 int lc[N], rc[N];\n', '9 int res[N];\n', '10 string str;\n', '11 void dfs(int v) {\n', '12   if (lc[v] != -1) dfs(lc[v]);\n', '13   ord[tim] = v;\n', '14   in[v] = tim++;\n', '15   if (rc[v] != -1) dfs(rc[v]);\n', '16 }\n', '17 void solve(int v, int& rem) {\n', '18   int la = -1;\n', '19   int cur = v;\n', '20   for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 string s;\n', '4 int n, k, t, cnt[2001];\n', '5 unsigned long long x;\n', '6 int main() {\n', '7   cin >> t;\n', '8   while (t--) {\n', '9     cin >> n >> k >> x;\n', '10     cin >> s;\n', '11     string news = """";\n', '12     int len = -1;\n', '13     for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n', '14       if (i == 0) {\n', '15         news += s[i];\n', ""16         if (s[i] == '*') {\n"", '17           len++;\n', '18           cnt[len] = k;\n', '19         } else {\n', '20           len++;\n', '21           cnt[len] = 0;\n', '22         }\n', '23       } else {\n', ""24         if (s[i] == s[i - 1] && s[i] == '*') {\n"", '25           cnt[len] += k;\n', '26         } else {\n', '27           news += s[i];\n', ""28           if (s[i] == '*') {\n"", '29             len++;\n', '30             cnt[len] = k;\n', '31           } else {\n', '32             len++;\n', '33             cnt[len] = 0;\n', '34           }\n', '35         }\n', '36       }\n', '37     }\n', '38     len = news.size();\n', '39     unsigned long long tt = 1, vt = 0;\n', '40     vector<unsigned long long> thutu;\n', '41     thutu.push_back(1);\n', '42     for (int i = len - 1; i >= 0; i--) {\n', '43       unsigned long long prett = tt;\n', '44       if (cnt[i] > 0) {\n', '45         tt = tt * (cnt[i] + 1);\n', '46         thutu.push_back(tt);\n', '47         if (x / prett <= cnt[i]) {\n', '48           vt = i;\n', '49           break;\n', '50         }\n', '51       }\n', '52     }\n', '53     for (int i = 0; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 int main() {\n', '4   ios::sync_with_stdio(0);\n', '5   cin.tie(0);\n', '6   int t;\n', '7   cin >> t;\n', '8   while (t--) {\n', '9     int n;\n', '10     cin >> n;\n', '11     vector<int> a(n + 1, 0);\n', '12     for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) cin >> a[i];\n', '13     const int inf = (1 << 30);\n', '14     vector<array<int, 2>> dp(n + 1, {inf, inf});\n', '15     vector<array<int, 2>> p(n + 1, {-1, -1});\n', '16     dp[1] = {-inf, -inf};\n', '17     auto upd = [&](int i, int j, int lim, int u) {\n', '18       if (lim < dp[i][j]) {\n', '19         dp[i][j] = lim;\n', '20         p[i][j] = u;\n', '21       }\n', '22     };\n', '23     for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) {\n', '24       for (int j = 0; j < 2; j++) {\n', '25         if (dp[i][j] == inf) continue;\n', '26         int x = (j ? "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int maxn = 23;\n', '4 const int mod = 998244353;\n', '5 const int INF = 0x3f3f3f3f;\n', '6 const long long llINF = 0x3f3f3f3f3f3f3f3f;\n', '7 long long make_compiler_happy() { return INF ^ 3 ^ maxn ^ mod ^ llINF; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 inline int read() {\n', '4   int ans = 0, f = 1;\n', '5   char c = getchar();\n', ""6   while (c > '9' || c < '0') {\n"", ""7     if (c == '-') f = -1;\n"", '8     c = getchar();\n', '9   }\n', ""10   while (c >= '0' && c <= '9') {\n"", ""11     ans = (ans << 1) + (ans << 3) + c - '0';\n"", '12     c = getchar();\n', '13   }\n', '14   return ans * f;\n', '15 }\n', '16 inline void write(int x) {\n', ""17   if (x < 0) putchar('-'), x = -x;\n"", '18   if (x / 10) write(x / 10);\n', ""19   putchar((char)(x % 10) + '0');\n"", '20 }\n', '21 template <typename T>\n', '22 inline T Abs(T a) {\n', '23   return a > 0 ? a : -a;\n', '24 };\n', '25 template <typename T, typename TT>\n', '26 inline T Min(T a, TT b) {\n', '27   return a < b ? a : b;\n', '28 }\n', '29 template <typename T, typename TT>\n', '30 inline T Max(T a, TT b) {\n', '31   return a < b ? b : a;\n', '32 }\n', '33 const int N = 1e4 + 5;\n', '34 int t, n, m, a[N], c[N], ans;\n', '35 char s[15][N];\n', '36 pair<int, int> b[N];\n', '37 signed main() {\n', '38   t = read();\n', '39   while (t--) {\n', '40     n = read();\n', '41     m = read();\n', '42     for (int i = 1; "['1 #include <bits/stdc++.h>\n', '2 using namespace std;\n', '3 const int N = (int)2e5 + 50, LOGN = 17;\n', '4 const int INF = (int)1e9;\n', '5 int n, k;\n', '6 int ord[N], in[N], tim = 0;\n', '7 char las[N];\n', '8 int lc[N], rc[N];\n', '9 int res[N];\n', '10 string str;\n', '11 void dfs(int v) {\n', '12   if (lc[v] != -1) dfs(lc[v]);\n', '13   ord[tim] = v;\n', '14   in[v] = tim++;\n', '15   if (rc[v] != -1) dfs(rc[v]);\n', '16 }\n', '17 void solve(int v, int& rem) {\n', '18   int la = -1;\n', '19   int cur = v;\n', '20   for (int i = 0;
